{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff5eaf3920","title":"和张治中的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e9a6087631","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"ff5eaf3920"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a611b74ffa","type":"title","text":"和张治中的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ff5eaf3920"},{"id":"55f88ec028","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：解放军将由兰州和青海分两路向新疆进军，希望你去电给新疆军政负责人叫他们起义为好。我从新疆得到的情况，只要你去电，他们是一定照办的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ff5eaf3920"},{"id":"1940992033","type":"paragraph","text":"张治中：我早有此意，不过我在五月间曾接陶时岳、包尔汉来电问候我的情况以后，音讯就断绝了，现在我还不知道怎样和他们取得联系。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ff5eaf3920"},{"id":"c5dd4b94c0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：我们已经在伊型建立电台，你的电报可以先拍到伊型再转迪化，我可以告知在伊型负责的邓力群。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ff5eaf3920"}],"page":{"id":"b6b51684cf","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ff5eaf3920","start":227,"end":227}}}},"__N_SSG":true}